My suggestion is to wait.  Once you outfit your guild with SS to the max, or close to it, continue on to NTOV and some really nice caster gear with hps AND mana will start dropping. You are sitting at 1700hps and 3800mana, that's really not that shabby considering. <br>
<br>
change out your mask. get a muishroom veil, gives 65mana or so.  or something else. you don't need see invis all the time, granted it is handy but *shrug*<br>
wear velium BD bracers, they give more mana and better saves. no reason to have extended range unless you soloing.<br>
considering you are in HoT getting pieces for SS armor your guild should be almost ready to do Velk's. Get some BoBC.<br>
<br>
Other then that your gear is nice and you'll do fine going into NTOV<br>
